            <div class="tactic-title">Prep Time Strategy</div>
            <p>Don't frontload all your prep. Recommended distribution:</p>
            <ol>
                <li><strong>Before Constructive:</strong> 2-3 minutes (outline your case, plan opening)</li>
                <li><strong>Before Rebuttals:</strong> 2-3 minutes each (plan attacks, prioritize responses)</li>
                <li><strong>Reserve:</strong> Keep 1-2 minutes for emergencies (unexpected arguments, needed recovery)</li>
            </ol>
            <p><strong>Common mistake:</strong> Using 5+ minutes before your constructive, leaving nothing for rebuttals when you need it most.</p>
