            <h4>Pre-Tournament Self-Assessment</h4>
            <p>Before your first (or next) tournament, rate yourself 1-5 on: (1) Constructive speech structure, (2) Cross-examination questioning, (3) Cross-examination answering, (4) Rebuttal prioritization, (5) Closing summary. Identify your lowest score. That's your practice priority. After the tournament, rate again and compare.</p>
