            <h4>Timed Speech Drill</h4>
            <p>Pick any topic you have an opinion on. Set a timer for exactly 5 minutes. Deliver a constructive speech hitting the time template: hook by 0:20, contention 1 by 2:00, contention 2 by 3:20, summary by 4:45. Record yourself and review. Where did you run long? Where did you have time to spare? Repeat until the timing is natural.</p>
